### ============================================
### QUERY LENDER HISTORY TESTS
### ============================================

### Query all history for John Doe
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId1}}/history
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Query all history for Jane Smith
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId2}}/history
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Query all history for Bob Wilson
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId3}}/history
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Query history for John Doe filtered by type PAID_IN_FULL
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId1}}/history?type=PAID_IN_FULL
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Query history for Jane Smith filtered by type FORGIVEN
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId2}}/history?type=FORGIVEN
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Query history for Bob Wilson filtered by value range
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId3}}/history?minValue=75&maxValue=300
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Query history for Jane Smith with combined filters (date range + type)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId2}}/history?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31&type=PAID_IN_FULL
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Query history for Bob Wilson with all filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/lenders/{{lenderId3}}/history?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31&minValue=100&maxValue=500&type=PAID_IN_FULL
Accept: {{contentType}}